description:
Manual games allow you to set custom check locations and custom item names that will be rolled into a multiworld.
This allows any variety of game -- PC, console, board games, Microsoft Word memes... really anything -- to be part of a multiworld randomizer.
The key component to including these games is some level of manual restriction. Since the items are not actually withheld from the player,
the player must manually refrain from using these gathered items until the tracker shows that they have been acquired or sent.

V.1.1.0.description:
### Dead by Daylight Manual V.1.1.0 both English / Français versions
You can now choose : 
- Which Survivors you have and how many Survivors you need to win with
- If you have to do Missions in the fog
- If you have to earn progressives items
- If you have to earn progressives add-ons
- If you have to earn progressives offerings
- If you have to earn and win with all perks
- If you have to earn and win with base perks

Vous pouvez maintenant choisir :
- Les Survivants que vous voulez ainsi que le nombre de Survivants requis pour gagner
- Si vous devez faire des petits objectifs
- Si vous devez recevoir les items progressifs
- Si vous devez recevoir les accessoires progressifs
- Si vous devez recevoir les offrandes progressifs
- Si vous devez recevoir et gagner avec toutes les perks
- Si vous devez recevoir et gagner avec les perks de base
